## ❗ Problem Being Solved

Studios often lack structured prioritisation, leading to inefficient workflows.
There are delays delays in delivery timelines due to uneven workload distribution and dependencies from artists.

**Pain points addressed:**
- No data-driven prioritisation
- Manual scheduling inefficiency
- High-risk scenes not identified early

